brand.disclaimerTextAU:
AUSTRALIA PRICE LIST (AUD) - ALL PRICES & DETAILS ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE WITHOUT NOTICE.
ALL PRICES SHOWN EXCLUDE GST.
SAMPLES: Column 1 prices are for samples and small quantities only plus minimum order freight charge of $36.00.
NO DECORATION IS AVAILABLE FROM C-3 APPAREL FOR THIS RANGE OF PRODUCTS
ORDER TERMS & CONDITIONS: See our Ordering Information/T&C’s on our website for more information.
DELIVERY CHARGES: Column 2 to 4 Prices include delivery costs from Europe directly to metro areas / capital cities within Australia.
REMOTE LOCATION SURCHARGE: Column 1 to 4 Either $30.00 per order or $0.60 per kg whichever is greater on top.
See our Ordering T&C’s for DHL link to check if your postcode is a remote location.
